Package: competitiontoolbox
Type: Package
Title: Additional Tools for Antitrust and Trade Practitioners
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Charles Taragin
Maintainer: Charles Taragin <ctaragin@ftc.gov>
Depends: antitrust (>= 0.99.11), trade (>= 0.5.4)
Description: A package that helps launch a shiny interface for both
    the trade and antitrust packages. The shiny interface provides 
    users with ability to calibrate and simulate horizontal mergers
    using many of the supply and demand models included in the 
    antitrust package as well as the simulate the effects of 
    traffics in the trade package.
    Use four spaces when indenting paragraphs within the Description.
License: Unlimited
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
